            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英偉達投資的Lumentum因AI需求訂單已排至2028年——彭博社",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.130ucTWhmOBTs8AJXOEJw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA9Q076_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com——據彭博社週四報導,Lumentum Holdings Inc(NASDAQ:LITE)表示,來自人工智能產業對其光學元件的需求預計將使其訂單簿排滿至2028年。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家獲得英偉達投資的公司正看到來自美國超大規模雲端服務商的需求加速增長,且仍面臨滿足需求的困難,彭博社報導稱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Lumentum製造光學和光子產品,特別是用於通訊和網絡應用,被視為該板塊的領導者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近年來,隨著華爾街最大的科技公司擴建更多數據中心基礎設施,對其網絡產品的需求急劇上升,使Lumentum的股價在過去一年中上漲了約1500%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-35391397-5ee8-3c6a-a9d4-32466b1e1173-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">光學電路和收發器是AI數據中心的關鍵組件,因為它們需要超快的處理速度。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Lumentum於2015年從JDSU分拆出來,並在2026年3月初獲得英偉達20億美元的投資。該投資還附帶英偉達數十億美元的採購承諾。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%81%89%E9%81%94%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%9A%84lumentum%E5%9B%A0ai%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E5%B7%B2%E6%8E%92%E8%87%B32028%E5%B9%B4-%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E7%A4%BE-055850552.html",
