            "title": "財經｜摯達科技(02650)將獲納入深港通及滬港通合資格股票名單",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜摯達科技(02650)將獲納入深港通及滬港通合資格股票名單\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"財經｜摯達科技\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:財經｜摯達科技;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/財經｜摯達科技\">財經｜摯達科技</a>(02650)將獲納入深港通及滬港通合資格股票名單</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摯達科技(02650)公布，公司H股已自今年3月9日起獲納入恒生綜合指數成份股，並將自今年4月10日起分別獲納入深港通及滬港通港股通的合資格股票名單。公司指，預期是次納入將進一步擴大公司的投資者基礎，並有望增加H股的交易流通量。</p></div>",
